text: And another to Bell. Scots 2/7 off 7
Belly strikes early with a sharp caught and bowled!
Scots have won the toss and are batting here at the Buchanan. Good luck to all teams today.
Kings pass our total in the 17th over, two wickets down. Well played Kings. In 2s we fell short in the chase.
Kings are chasing 81 in 1sts. In 2nds we have bowled out kings for 149
Kings on top. We are 7/63 off 26 with Sigi and Joel at the wicket.
And we're off! 1s batting at Kings, 1/27 in the 10th. At Stanmore the 2s are bowling and have Kings 1/27. Good luck boys.
2nds need 5 more with 4 wickets in hand. Henry C there on 70*
All out on the final ball for 154. Tight finish and Joe & Ben H unlucky not to get us across the line. Well played New & Joeys
2nds are 2/79 off 25. Henry C and Gus at the crease. Cal last out - was hitting them well
5/123 in the 39th. Nick C last out after an excellent partnership with Tim P
Thanks for hosting us @JoeysCricket the facilities looking superb and the chicken for lunch got the thumbs up from the boys pic.twitter.com/E1ghvoxFGI
3/60 with Condon and Whitnall at the crease. Ned last out for 41
Solid start to 1sts chase . 1/31 off 11
Joeys finish 9/156. Wickets spread around with 2 to Leung at the end.
2nds have Joeys 3/70 off 32. Ward and Walton have all the wickets. The spin twins!
6/102 after some Whitnall magic. D'Arcy back into the attack pic.twitter.com/a7DBXPcxrT
Drinks. Joeys 4/73 off 34. Wickets Bell x2, D'Arcy & Barnet. Good catch by Phillips for last wicket
Newington bowling in both fixtures. In 1s Joeys 3/35 good spells by Bell and D'Arcy. 2s no wickets yet but Barnes looking dangerous
Notables from last weekend's fixtures against Shore. 1s: Leung 50, Whitnall 46, Barnet-H 4/30 2s: Burton 45. 2 losses but plenty to improve
